  "informal_statement": "For any natural number n >= 4, 2^n <= n!.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n starting at base case 4. Base case 2^4 = 16 <= 24 = 4! holds by decide. Step case uses 2 <= m + 1 and 2^m <= m! to deduce 2^(m+1) <= (m+1)!.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem two_pow_le_factorial_four' : ∀ (n : ℕ), 4 ≤ n → 2 ^ n ≤ Nat.factorial n",
